{"tid":2180525,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葉劉：港人如何出境非問題 不會構成罪行 不存在非法出境","createTime":"2020-08-30T02:14:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T02:26:02.000Z","uid":362199,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a222facdd8c8fe3c1404ad79f105955492d29736","tid":2180525,"uid":362199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T02:14:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20160202/s00001/1454373702205/%E3%80%90%E6%9B%B8%E5%BA%975%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%B1%E8%B9%A4%E3%80%91%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%87%BA%E5%A2%83%E9%9D%9E%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C-%E4%B8%8D%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E5%87%BA%E5%A2%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20160202%2Fs00001%2F1454373702205%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%259B%25B8%25E5%25BA%25975%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%25B9%25A4%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%2591%2589%25E5%258A%2589-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A6%2582%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25A2%2583%25E9%259D%259E%25E5%2595%258F%25E9%25A1%258C-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25AD%2598%25E5%259C%25A8%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25A2%2583&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLIDkkQuUBcdRTUhzZaMUkok%3D&h=ec6027f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20160202%2Fs00001%2F1454373702205%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%259B%25B8%25E5%25BA%25975%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%25B9%25A4%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%2591%2589%25E5%258A%2589-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A6%2582%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25A2%2583%25E9%259D%259E%25E5%2595%258F%25E9%25A1%258C-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25AD%2598%25E5%259C%25A8%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25A2%2583&h=9f5d12ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20160202/s00001/1454373702205/%E3%80%90%E6%9B%B8%E5%BA%975%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%B1%E8%B9%A4%E3%80%91%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%87%BA%E5%A2%83%E9%9D%9E%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C-%E4%B8%8D%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E5%87%BA%E5%A2%83</a><br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀今早於商台節目解釋，入境條例中「無一條罪行叫無持有效旅行證件離境」；至於李波沒用回鄉卡出境，她指「出境（香港）唔係睇回鄉卡，入境（內地）先睇回鄉卡，你無回鄉卡唔關我事架。陸地或港口口岸出境，唔睇你回鄉卡，睇你有無身分證之嘛」。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀強調，香港永久居民如何出境「唔會係一個問題」，「睇唔到會點樣構成罪行。無非法出境說法」。她又說，即使港人在外地遺失了身分證，「都好容易入返來（香港）」，只要向入境處說自己遺失了身分證便可。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀又說，如離境時不接受入境人員檢查，可能觸犯入境條例；不經口岸進入禁區，亦可能犯禁區條例，但重申「無永久性居民未經許可出入境條例，係無嘅」。<br />\n<br />\n入境處長陳國基昨亦稱，香港永久居民以自己方式出入境不會被控「非法出入境」，但可能涉及違反其他條例。"},{"pid":"111ee87c433e89a830e22e42475b27cf44b89d92","tid":2180525,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T02:17:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a316e89071d231bbd7c358665aa1f1e9f05d0f3","tid":2180525,"uid":292007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T02:18:40.000Z","msg":"拉9佢犯国安法未？"},{"pid":"adf32c6f3fc3e7f64f8083fa4b6ee8092dc2181d","tid":2180525,"uid":306664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T02:18:52.000Z","msg":"可能涉及違反其他條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />李波告左味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />2016年啦喎"},{"pid":"dfcf7317c96608bf02c850fa71bda379c29620f4","tid":2180525,"uid":1159,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T02:19:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入境處長陳國基昨亦稱，香港永久居民以自己方式出入境不會被控「